	<h4>3 Customer Service Trends to Watch at Dreamforce</h4>
<p>The importance of customer experience is more than clear — it’s a mandate. Though it’s expected, quality customer experience is hard to achieve and maintain as you grow. An important question becomes how to handle speed,relevance and personalization of customer engagement at scale. Given this situation, Alan Berkson explores three themes he expects to play out at Dreamforce.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.socialmediatoday.com/content/3-customer-service-trends-watch-dreamforce" target="_blank">Continue Reading </a></p></div>



