	<h4>Google Capital jumps into $31M round for Freshdesk</h4>
<p>Freshdesk successfully pitched the investors at Google Capital, the mid- to late-stage venture capital wing of the tech giant, which poured millions into the help-desk business alongside the startup’s existing investors, Freshdesk announced today. Altogether, Freshdesk pulled in $31 million in exchange for an undisclosed amount of equity, bringing its total financing to $44 million.</p>
