	<h3>The Customer Support Hierarchy of Needs</h3>
<p>If you looked at how different organizations handled their customer support, the maturity of their operations, and the problems they were trying to solve, companies fall into 4 distinct strata — from a state of chaos, all the way up to the point where their support is perfectly aligned with their business goals. And as you move up the chain towards alignment, the number of companies in each strata steadily falls. I call this the Great Pyramid of Support Needs.</p>
