<p>The platform enables agents to win points and earn badges for completing customer support tasks, including customizable games that can be created to align with business goals, as highlighted in the video above. Agents can level up from “Support Newbies” to “Help Gurus” and earn all kinds of digital bling, such as the “Speed Racer” and “Customer Wow Champ” trophies. Potentially the most coveted trophy of all, is the “Most Valuable Player” trophy, awarded monthly to top scorers.</p>
